blog.name: pokegodsandmissingno
blog.title: P̵o̵K̸é̴G̸o̸D̷s̸ and Frightful Things to Come?
blog.description: There is a growing desire and expectation of humans here on Earth in making full contact with PoKéMoN who are still unknown. Back in 1995, when I saw my first UPM (Unindexed Pocket Monster), I found out very quickly that other people thought you were totally crazy if you said you saw such things. The world has changed quite a bit since then when I was a child. In fact, in late 1997, a poll taken in Kanto shows that for the first time ever, more than fifty percent of residents now believe in PokéGODS's. Since then, there have been polls that put the figure at over eighty percent or more.

summary: Chapter 8 was the first time I felt brave enough to outline the characters’ silhouettes and background lineart in white. The...
caption:
Chapter 8 was the first time I felt brave enough to outline the characters’ silhouettes and background lineart in white. The lineart for NOICE is done traditionally and is scanned in, and since I don’t feel very confident with digital lineart, I was very hesitant to try anything like this. But for the sake of character silhouettes and background details being more easily seen during a night scene, I wanted to try.

I’m glad I did. ; v ;

summary: My energy is kinda low for full-on thoughts post for SM088 atm, sorry. It’s possible I’ll skip making it this time around. But I...
body:
My energy is kinda low for full-on thoughts post for SM088 atm, sorry. It’s possible I’ll skip making it this time around. But I did enjoy the episode, the subtitles helped me understand the episode much better. We’re so gonna be seeing Lusamine and Burnet decipher the mural (I’m so happy) and… somehow I never made the connection with Necrozma’s back having the same symbol as the Ultra Necrozma symbol. I have been so blind lol.

Really action-heavy episode, I really like how every single Ultra Guardian is battling against Necrozma here. And Lunala is so good *-* When Solgaleo goes to check on Lunala I go all awww. It’s so sweet.

I certainly want to know more about Matori’s squad too. I reaaaally hope they’ll be a thing during next year, maybe having clash with Skull Gang? I’m hoping for a Kuchinashi & Sakaki clash as well, that so needs to happen ~

There’s one thing that needs to be expected from Sun & Moon’s arcs, and that’s the fact that they’re pretty short, lasting about a month or two. Aether Arc is currently the longest one. But somehow I find it hard to believe that this will be all there is to Necrozma. I mean. We are seeing Ultra Necrozma next week, but the scene we saw in the preview appears to be an illusion shown by Naganadel/Agoyon. There’s no sign of a big battle. For the record, I don’t know anything about the last episode in this arc. Not a single thing. Except that the last episode is on Sep 13th. So I don’t know what has been confirmed to happen or stuff like that, and tbf I don’t want to know. It’s been awesome to come watching the Necrozma Arc episodes that’s aired now, and being so surprised by everything!

But on the preview still, we are so heading for Poni Trials soon. Sun & Moon has been good at giving hints at future plots, during previews or random lines in the episodes. Like, Kahunas/Island Queen and Kings talking about why Poni Island’s representor isn’t there? And Lychee saying it’s complicated?? Maybe… maybe the Kahuna had just passed on :o And now Hapu must rise to become one. I wonder how they’ll showcase her road to a Island Queen.

Also, I’m having the feeling that we won’t know a thing about what’s gonna happen after Necrozma Arc until September 13th when the last episode airs and we get the normal preview. Episode titles tend to come at the beginning of the month, and they tend to cover that month only. Some cases have had first episode of following month revealed but, I’m not counting on it. I’m really excited thou, it could have the same effect on me like Aether Arc reveal did. But it could also be just a filler-kind-of episode lol.

Anyway. Feel free to ask for further opinions on details if you like. I’m tired, it’s been a rough week.

Rock/Normal Type

Devon, She/Her, Asexual, In a state of sustained fear.

_Please only suggest things for fandoms I have shown recent interest in. I don't plan out my interests so questions about old fandoms and if I plan to draw for them are not appreciated. I am NEVER looking for new fandoms to get into, please DO NOT suggest new series for me, I promise you I HAVE heard already, I'll mention it on my own if I care.
